sequenceDiagram
    participant wiretap
    participant frontend
    participant backend
    participant P3 as api.example.com:8080
    wiretap->>frontend: GET /
    frontend->>backend: GET /api
    backend-->>frontend: 200 (80ms)
    backend->>P3: GET /ext
    P3-->>backend: 200 (30ms)
    frontend-->>wiretap: 200 (150ms)